<preface id="preface"> 
  <title>Preface</title> 
  <para> The <emphasis>Getting Started with Foresight Linux User Guide</emphasis> provides
	 a high level overview of using Foresight Linux, including the Conary package manager, for users new to Linux or Foresight. </para> 
  <sect1 id="preface-1"> 
	 <title>About This Guide</title> 
	 <para> The goal of the Getting Started with Foresight Linux User Guide is to provide
		a high level overview of using Foresight Linux, including the Conary package manager, for users new to Linux or Foresight.
		The User Guide also provides an overview of commonly used applications, customizing your new installation, adding and removing software, and tips on getting help.</para> 
  </sect1> 
